Nesse vídeo, você vai reviver um dos momentos mais insanos de Dragon Ball Z! Goku e Vegeta finalmente colocam os brincos Potara e se fundem, dando origem ao lendário Vegetto, o guerreiro mais poderoso da franquia até então! 💥

Majin Boo achou que estava no controle... mas mal sabia ele que estava prestes a ser humilhado por uma fusão que uniu o melhor dos dois Saiyajins! snippet.title: Dragon Ball Z The Entire Namek Saga but it's a Feature Length Film [Remaster]
snippet.description:
I took the second season of Dragon Ball Z Kai and turned it into a feature length film! Using clips from the Bardok special all the way through planet Namek's destruction. I compiled it all into a single (really long) movie. I also did the whole thing using a three way split of the original Kikuchi, Yamamoto and Faulconer scores with some additional songs. Now you can watch from the destruction of planet Vegeta through to the destruction planet of Namek in well under 4 hours. (Thats 11 hours faster than than the show, which you should also watch). This is a re-upload but it is also remastered. The sound is better balanced, the quality is HD, the cuts are smoother and a few small scenes where trimmed and/or added.

Songs in order:
When Worlds Collide - Powerman 5000
One Step Closer - Linkin Park
Goro Theme - MK(1995)
My Own Summer - Deftones
All Around Me - Flyleaf

localized.title: Dragon Ball Z The Entire Namek Saga but it's a Feature Length Film [Remaster]
localized.description:
I took the second season of Dragon Ball Z Kai and turned it into a feature length film! Using clips from the Bardok special all the way through planet Namek's destruction. I compiled it all into a single (really long) movie. I also did the whole thing using a three way split of the original Kikuchi, Yamamoto and Faulconer scores with some additional songs. Now you can watch from the destruction of planet Vegeta through to the destruction planet of Namek in well under 4 hours. (Thats 11 hours faster than than the show, which you should also watch). This is a re-upload but it is also remastered. The sound is better balanced, the quality is HD, the cuts are smoother and a few small scenes where trimmed and/or added.

Songs in order:
When Worlds Collide - Powerman 5000
One Step Closer - Linkin Park
Goro Theme - MK(1995)
My Own Summer - Deftones
All Around Me - Flyleaf

snippet.description:

The legacy continues.
In a new era of fan-made live-action power, Dragon Ball Z: Super Saiyan Awakening unites iconic heroes and villains across the Dragon Ball universe and beyond. From the terrifying rise of Cell and Majin Buu, to the resurrection of Frieza’s cruelty, Earth’s defenders must awaken their deepest powers to stop the chaos.

🔹 Saiyan Evolution Unleashed – Goku and Vegeta ascend through legendary Super Saiyan forms, unlocking Super Saiyan 3 to face overwhelming darkness.
🔹 Androids Reborn – Dr. Gero’s twisted creations return: Android 18, 17, and more. Perfect Cell reclaims his throne as Earth’s deadliest threat.
🔹 Majin Madness – Babidi returns, summoning Buu and unleashing warriors like Dabura, Yakon, and Pui Pui into the fight.
🔹 Heroes United – Gohan, Piccolo, Krillin, and even Bulma’s family join the resistance. Capsule Corp is ground zero for the final stand.
🔹 GT Echoes – A glimpse into the future: Goten and his mysterious friend Valese step into a world shaped by past battles.

👊 Z Fighters: Goku, Vegeta, Gohan, Piccolo, Krillin, Trunks, Goten
⚔️ Villains: Frieza (Final Form & Golden), Perfect Cell, Majin Buu, Babidi, Dabura, Yakon, Pui Pui, Android 17 & 18
🏢 Locations: Capsule Corporation, Babidi’s Spaceship, Ruined Earth Cities
🔥 Transformations: Super Saiyan, Super Saiyan 2, Super Saiyan 3

💥 Will awakening be enough to stop destruction… or is this just the beginning?
